        "cooked": "<p>Generally, you‚Äôre describing chat folders, which are live on Android and Desktop. Though filtering by reply per sender, text string etc seems overly complicated and bloaty.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"yardena\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"72784\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/yardena/48/51912_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> yardena:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Views could have separate notification preferences which override those of the default view.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>You‚Äôre describing notification profiles, which is a feature on Android.</p>",
